Home > Music > VOTE: Who Is Your Favorite UK Rapper? VOTE: Who Is Your Favorite UK Rapper? 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz  35pm Cast your vote. UK's long-flourishing hip hop and grime communities have steadily made inroads into the American rap psyche over the course of the last decade. We have selected nine of the most popular British rappers, (excluding Slick Rick and MF Doom, both of whom were born in England and immigrated to New York in their youth) and we want you to pick your favorite. Our selections: Wiley Or is it someone else? Cast your vote below and sound off in the comments. < class="robots-nocontent" rel=""> Mar 22, 2017 at 05:35pm 1 View
